### Create user
POST http://localhost:8080/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "Riya Kapoor",
  "email": "riya@example.com",
  "passwordHash": "hash-riya",
  "preferredGenres": "music,food",
  "budgetPreference": "4000"
}

### Create venue
POST http://localhost:8080/api/venues
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Night Pulse Stage",
  "address": "West Festival Grounds",
  "latitude": 19.08,
  "longitude": 72.88,
  "capacity": 2500,
  "venueType": "stage"
}

### Create event
POST http://localhost:8080/api/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Midnight Fusion",
  "description": "Late night live set",
  "category": "music",
  "startTime": "2026-06-27T22:00:00",
  "endTime": "2026-06-27T23:30:00",
  "price": 1100,
  "score": 87,
  "venueId": 1
}

### Get recommendations
GET http://localhost:8080/api/recommendations/events?userId=1

### Generate schedule
POST http://localhost:8080/api/schedules/generate?userId=1

### Get organizer overview
GET http://localhost:8080/api/analytics/overview

### Get all events
GET http://localhost:8080/api/events